Script ğŸ“

logo par railway officers ki dada giri bdhti hi ja rahi hai jaha par railway me general aur sleeper coaches ko kam kiya ja raha hai to dusri taraf railway me kiraya bhi badhaya ja raha hai 

jaha par bharat me kayi trains time par nahi chal paati na usme koi saaf safai hoti hai jisse aam aadmi ke saath saath middle class bhi piss raha hai

ek student intercity train k general coach me safar krke aata hai aur ticket nahi kharidta kyuki uska uska next stop 25 minute me hi aa jata hai, aur bhid se bahre hue dabbe jisme ek per rakhne ki jagah bhi nahi hoti usme jaise taise chad jata hai 

jab wo apne destination stop pr utarta hai aur bridge se station k bahar jata hai to use ticket collector pakad leta hai 

uss student ko realise hota hai aur wo challan banane ke liye taiyar ho jata hai, TC usse uska adhaar id mangta hai uss student k pass physical  card nahi hota to wo apne digilocker ko open krke adhaar id show krta hai, 

TC apne haath me phone leta hai aur dekh kr uss student ka phone apne pocket me rkh leta hai wo student apna phone TC se mangta hai to TC phone dene se mana kr deta hai 

student bolta hai ki mene challan banane k liye mana nahi kiya to mera phone kyu rakha apne pass, aapke pass koi right nahi hai meri personnel property chhin k rkhne ka.

bar bar wo student uss TC se apna phone mangta hai pr wo TC phone nahi deta, uss TC n koi ID card bhi nahi pehna hota 

wo student hyper ho jata hai aur uss TC se rudely aur tezz awaaz me bat krne lgta ki naam aur id btao apni pr wo apna naam bhi nahi btata,

wo TC bolta hai apna challan bnwa lo fir m de dunga, wo student bolta hai ki me challan banwa lunga phle RPF ko bulao, aur wo student sb k samne uss TC se rudely baat krta hai aur RPF ko call krne ko bolta hai ki uss TC n uska phone kaise rkh liya, aur wo TC apna name aur id bhi nahi btata..

bht shorr krne p wo TC RPF ko bulata hai aur TC apni kahani RPF ko btata hai aur student ko without ticket janne k bd TC ka favor krne lgta hai aur misbehave krke chawki m leke jata hai 

uss student k request krne k bd wo RPF student ki puri bt sunta hai aur TC ko bol k challan banwata hai lekin wo RPF wala TC k khne p jbrdsti apology letter likhwaata hai last m dusre RPF man n TC se naam puchha to usne naam Mohd Armaan btaya..

issme aapki kya ray hai, btayiye, Dhanywaad
